  ],
  "remarks": "Pavel Ezubov is the cousin of Oleg Deripaska, owner of the Russian Machines industrial conglomerate which includes the Military Industrial Company, a major arms and military equipment provider to the Russian armed forces. Oleg Deripaska has transferred large assets to his cousin Pavel Ezubov, including several properties in France, via a holding company owned by Ezubov, a hotel in Lech, Austria, through the Russian-based holding company Gost Hotel Management LLC owned by Ezubov and the control of the company Terra Limited. Pavel Ezubov is therefore associated with Oleg Deripaska.",
